spec_data.Name: perl-Test-Time
spec_data.Description:
Test::Time can be used to test modules that deal with time. Once you use
this module, all references to time and sleep will be internalized. You can
set custom time by passing time => number after the use statement.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sun 06 Aug 2017 04:31:10 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Overrides the time() and sleep() core functions for testing
